//젠코딩 하는 법

article*4>h3{타이틀$} 

입력

<article>
  <h3>타이틀1</h3>
</article>
<article>
  <h3>타이틀2</h3>
</article>
<article>
  <h3>타이틀3</h3>
</article>
<article>
  <h3>타이틀4</h3>
</article>



